While practicing my skill, I would only attempt 1pick per mob, regardless of the result. No one was the wiser, and the occaisional big pick of coin would just have the group thinking the mob was a cheap ass. <p><CENTER>Heggley <BR>Level 50 buttling Rogue<BR><a href=http://www.soulcadre.com><u><b>Soul Cadre</lnk></b></u></CENTER>
